{"tid":2074252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【不用審判，立即凍結】微信用戶30萬資金突然被騰訊凍結　騰訊：騰訊擁有所有權","createTime":"2020-06-22T03:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T03:36:35.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc4e9e5938a880573f7f08b1063207a1b562dde","tid":2074252,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:27:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef44b27a2f25.68074067.jpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=fpimgs%2Es3%2Dap%2Dsoutheast%2D1%2Eamazonaws%2Ecom%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef44b27a2f25%2E68074067%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dfpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef44b27a2f25.68074067.jpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dfpimgs%252Es3%252Dap%252Dsoutheast%252D1%252Eamazonaws%252Ecom%252Fuul%252F202006%252F200621%252F5eef44b27a2f25%252E68074067%252Ejpg&h=0ab08ed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日根據國內媒體報導，福州一位經營廣告公司的王女士，平常生活大多時都會利用微信進行交易。近日因她的賬戶涉嫌違規交易，被限制部分收款功能，隨​更​後直接將其賬戶中近30萬資金凍結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4093ddb941.65132393.jpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=fpimgs%2Es3%2Dap%2Dsoutheast%2D1%2Eamazonaws%2Ecom%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4093ddb941%2E65132393%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dfpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4093ddb941.65132393.jpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dfpimgs%252Es3%252Dap%252Dsoutheast%252D1%252Eamazonaws%252Ecom%252Fuul%252F202006%252F200621%252F5eef4093ddb941%252E65132393%252Ejpg&h=a60a54a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n王女士得知帳戶被凍結後，即時聯繫騰訊客服，並提供企業信息、訂單信息、身份信息等資料，但申訴十多次得到的回座仍是&quot;維持原判&quot;，甚至她都不知道自己犯下哪條所謂的違規交易。<br />\n其後王女士只好向媒體求助，在記者的協助下再次跟騰訊聯絡，竟然得到的回覆居然是「用戶對微信只有使用權，而騰訊卻擁有所有權」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.weserv.nl/?url=fpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/uul/202006/200621/5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg&amp;w=680&amp;output=jpg&amp;q=80&amp;we&amp;errorredirect=fpimgs%2Es3%2Dap%2Dsoutheast%2D1%2Eamazonaws%2Ecom%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4203a17e02%2E90466298%2Ejpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.weserv.nl%2F%3Furl%3Dfpimgs.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Fuul%2F202006%2F200621%2F5eef4203a17e02.90466298.jpg%26w%3D680%26output%3Djpg%26q%3D80%26we%26errorredirect%3Dfpimgs%252Es3%252Dap%252Dsoutheast%252D1%252Eamazonaws%252Ecom%252Fuul%252F202006%252F200621%252F5eef4203a17e02%252E90466298%252Ejpg&h=8e39800a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後在記者介入的第二天，王女士的帳戶就被解封，騰訊方面表示道歉，指今次事件是他們內部出錯，而今次事件曝光後，微信官方在微博上宣傳「請記好：你的錢就是你的錢！」但內地網民對今次事件相當不滿，因為騰訊是沒有權利凍結用戶的資金。"},{"pid":"031abe6e60cba2b75b4ef3ca2d7804e89df642ad","tid":2074252,"uid":36378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:30:38.000Z","msg":"錢是黨的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2308df5c6775f2ff26ec38d73327cc73d5c4d0","tid":2074252,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:30:44.000Z","msg":"真香"},{"pid":"953df8d7038a87e05616dd7e76a887dc53665e27","tid":2074252,"uid":15623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:35:30.000Z","msg":"後知後覺？"},{"pid":"bf4dd6ea43673f0f4cfd6b4605619e6bf60a2ad7","tid":2074252,"uid":279524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:36:35.000Z","msg":"唔怪知得狂升啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}